sequenceDiagram
    participant D as 延迟取消消费者
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant PSP as 支付渠道
    participant CB as 支付回调

    D->>P: CREATED/PAYING → CANCEL_PENDING
    P-->>D: 条件更新结果

    par 支付回调
        CB->>P: 插入payment_record
        CB->>P: CREATED/PAYING/CANCEL_PENDING → PAID
    and 关单流程
        D->>PSP: 幂等关闭支付单/查询支付结果
        PSP-->>D: PAID或CLOSED_UNPAID
        D->>P: CANCEL_PENDING → CANCELLED
    end

    Note over P: 所有状态更新都带前置状态条件
